<div class="question-panel panel panel--1">

  <h2 class="question-panel__heading question-panel__content">Ask a question</h2>
  <p class="question-panel__content">With Network of Innovators, you can get advice and answers to your questions from government and civic innovators worldwide. All you have to do is ask!</p>
  <% if user_signed_in? %>    
    <%= form_tag add_topic_path, method: 'put', class: "form form--negative question-panel__content question-panel__form" do %>
      <%= text_field_tag "topic-title", nil, placeholder: "Ask your question" %>
      <%= text_area_tag "topic-text", nil, placeholder: "Provide more details about your question" %>
      <div class="select select--negative">
        <%= select_tag "topic-category", 
          options_for_select(@categories.map { |cat| cat['slug'] }), { :include_blank => 'Choose a Category' } %>
      </div>
      <%= button_tag "Post", type: 'submit', class: "button button--full button--main-color" %> 

    <% end %>
  <% else %>
    <%= link_to fetch_sign_up_path, :remote => true do %>
      <p class="question-panel__content"><button class="button button--full button--main-color" type="submit">Sign Up</button></p>
    <% end %>
    
    <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
  </form>


  <% end %>
  <div class="question-panel__action question-panel__content js-panel-action">
    <h4 class="question-panel__action__title js-open-action-panel">How it works</h4>
    <div class="question-panel__action__content ">
      <p>When you ask a question, it will post to the <a href="http://discuss.networkofinnovators.org" target="_blank">discussion forum</a> and be shown here in the activity feed where government and civic innovators worldwide will be able to see and help. A GovLab team member will also personally work on tracking down relevant people or information for you and will respond to your post.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
